{"heading":"The gospel comes both in word and in power.","number":1,"verseCount":10,"verses":[[1,["Paul, and ",["Silvanus",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 15:34 (32–34)","nt/acts/15.34"],"; ",["2 Cor. 1:19","nt/2-cor/1.19"],"; ",["1 Pet. 5:12","nt/1-pet/5.12"],"."]]],", and ",["Timotheus",["study-note-ref","b",[["Acts 16:1 (1–2)","nt/acts/16.1"],"; ",["18:5 (1, 5)","nt/acts/18.5"],"; ",["1 Thes. 3:2 (2, 6)","nt/1-thes/3.2"],"."]]],", ",["unto",["study-note-ref","c",["JST 1 Thes. 1:1 … servants of God the Father and the Lord Jesus Christ, unto the church of the Thessalonians; grace unto you …"]]]," the ",["church",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Jesus Christ, Head of the Church","tg/jesus-christ-head-of-the-church"],"."]]]," of the ",["Thessalonians",["study-note-ref","e",[["Acts 17:1 (1, 11)","nt/acts/17.1"],"."]]]," ",["which is",["clarity-word"]]," in God the Father and ",["in",["clarity-word"]]," the Lord Jesus Christ: Grace ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," unto you, and peace, from God our Father, and the Lord Jesus Christ."]],[2,["We give ",["thanks",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 46:32","dc-testament/dc/46.32"],"."]]]," to God always for you all, making mention of you in our prayers;"]],[3,["Remembering without ceasing your work of ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Thes. 5:8","nt/1-thes/5.8"],"; ",["James 2:17","nt/james/2.17"],"."]]],", and ",["labour",["study-note-ref","b",[["Heb. 6:10","nt/heb/6.10"],"."]]]," of love, and ",["patience",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Patience","tg/patience"],"."]]]," of hope in our Lord Jesus Christ, in the sight of God and our Father;"]],[4,["Knowing, brethren ",["beloved",["study-note-ref","a",["GR beloved of God, your election."]]],", your ",["election",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Election","tg/election"],"."]]]," of God."]],[5,["For our ",["gospel",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Gospel","tg/gospel"],"."]]]," ",["came",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Thes. 2:1","nt/1-thes/2.1"],"."]]]," not unto you in ",["word",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Co